归纳和总结。「在考试前，我通常都会将老师拓展的新题型，以及总结的模型在心里过一遍，这样就可以在考试时迅速反应出所考的知识点。」郭雨坤说。 面对高考这样的大型考试，郭雨坤也给学弟学妹们分享了自己的经验。在他看来，心态是最重要的。「在考试中，要有自己的节奏，如果在小考中出现失利，也不要紧张。」郭雨坤说，考试中如果遇到自己不会的题目，可以暂时跳过，一定要静下心来。 除了对自己的学习有规划，平日里，郭雨坤也有自己的爱好——打球、骑车，平时自己也会利用一切可以锻炼的时间去锻炼。 对于自己想要报考的学校，郭雨坤坦言，自己想报考清华大学或者北京大学，专业方面，他倾向与微电子有关的专业。四川绵阳一理科考生高考 710 分，其中数学满分：看到分数很震惊 - 上游新闻 汇聚向上的力量"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-05fe14c8efb8bd7cbde533ab172c919b_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "126 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/659728381"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iv7/4gdWc1pMCEAMaCTEwODg4NDEzMiCh9+KzBjAAOE9AC3IJNjU5NzI4MzgxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1719288657.692328", "card_id": "Q_659627900", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 151}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "一个公司老板经常对员工说：「我用你你就是人才，不用你你啥也不是。」这样对待的人才的观点对吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a5abf4482900a7671a5b1403483cd576_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "122 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/659627900"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIv7/4gdWc1pMCEAMaCTEwODg2MTgyOSDR59uzBjAAOK4BQAxyCTY1OTYyNzkwMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1719288657.692565", "card_id": "Q_659746692", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.pn